pageContext.claim: “And no matter where you look, we have new deals going — new trade deals. And that's going to have a huge impact on our country. It's going to have a huge impact on jobs, going to open up markets that weren't opened before.”
pageContext.analysis: Trump has renegotiated some of the terms of NAFTA and some of the terms of a trade deal with South Korea. Those deals predated his administration, and those markets were already open to U.S. trade.
